snippet.title: Donkey Kong Country 3 on Game Boy Advance commercial
snippet.description:
The third installment of the classic Donkey Kong Country Saga ported to Game Boy Advance. I managed to find this in my old tape.

Aired during Disney´s House of Mouse on Toon Disney.

Donkey Kong Country 1, 2, and 3 and Game Boy Advance are all owned by Nintendo.

House of Mouse is owned by Disney.
